description:
🇨🇿 Během zimy byla na toto místo dovezena nová zemina (pravděpodobně z nějaké stavby) a rozhrnuta do plochy, takže místo bylo zcela bez vegetace. Je zajímavé, co zde první rok dominuje, kromě tohoto druhu ještě [*Thlaspi arvense*](https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/220428859) a [*Fumaria officinalis*](https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/220424161).
🇬🇧 During winter new soil was brought to this place (likely from a construction site) and spread out all over the place, so the place was completely without vegetation. It's interesting to observe which plants dominate in the first year, besides this species also [*Thlaspi arvense*](https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/220428859) and [*Fumaria officinalis*](https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/220424161).
empty insides, so not a Tripleurospermum
